name: Death Star Assault Squadron
Lore: 'Notoriety gained during the assaults on Ralltiir and Mon Calamari makes this the most feared squadron in the Empire. Defended the Death Star during the Battle of Yavin.',
Text: 'Permanent pilots aboard are •Darth Vader, •DS-61-2 and •DS-61-3, who provide total ability of 10 and add 9 to total power of •Vader''s Custom TIE, •Black 2 and •Black 3.',
